== 製作 ==
=== 開發 ===
2019年1月，[[Netflix|Netflix]]宣佈給予該劇整季預訂，第一季共八集，[[艾瑞克·赫瑟勒|艾瑞克·赫瑟勒]]擔當[[節目統籌|節目統籌]]、主創、首席編劇和執行製作人。這個項目屬於Netflix與{{link-en|21圈娛樂|21 Laps Entertainment}}的合約，由[[肖恩·利維|薛恩·李維]]擔任執行製作人。{{link-en|李·芭度葛|Leigh Bardugo}}、波亞·沙巴齊安（Pouya Shahbazian）、丹·萊文（Dan Levine）、丹·科恩（Dan Cohen）和喬許·貝瑞（Josh Barry）也擔任了執行製作人<ref name="series order">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/01/netflix-orders-shadow-and-bone-series-leigh-bardugo-grishaverse-fantasy-novels-1202532783/|title=Netflix Orders ''Shadow And Bone'' Series Based On Leigh Bardugo's Grishaverse Novels From Eric Heisserer & Shawn Levy|journal=Deadline|first1=Nellie|last1=Andreeva|first2=Denise|last2=Petski|date=2019-01-10|accessdate=2019-01-15|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201014101035/https://deadline.com/2019/01/netflix-orders-shadow-and-bone-series-leigh-bardugo-grishaverse-fantasy-novels-1202532783/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。作者李·芭度葛和節目主創艾瑞克·赫瑟勒討論了他們對該劇未來幾季的期望以及潛在的衍生劇<ref>{{Cite web |title=Shadow and Bone Season 2 Renewed on Netflix? and Other Details |url=https://dailyresearchplot.com/2021/04/26/shadow-and-bone-season-2-renewed-on-netflix-and-other-details/ |access-date=26 April 2021 |website=Daily Research Plot |archive-date=2021-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429021834/https://dailyresearchplot.com/2021/04/26/shadow-and-bone-season-2-renewed-on-netflix-and-other-details/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年6月7號，Netflix官方宣佈續訂第二季<ref name="Season2Renewal">{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/shadow-and-bone-renewed-season-2-netflix-1234963789/|title=‘Shadow and Bone’ Renewed for Second Season at Netflix|website=The Hollywood Reporter|first=Rick|last=Porter|date=June 7, 2021|access-date=June 7, 2021|archive-date=2021-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210607205335/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/shadow-and-bone-renewed-season-2-netflix-1234963789/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也將如同第一季由八集、長度為一小時組成<ref name="Season2Renewal"/>。

