chive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191003073138/https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/tv-news-roundup-netflix-shadow-and-bone-1203356620/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年12月18日，第二輪選角已宣布，卡拉漢·斯科格曼（Calahan Skogman）、{{link-en|佐伊·沃納梅克|Zoë Wanamaker}}、{{link-en|凱文·艾爾敦|Kevin Eldon}}、{{link-en|朱利安·科斯托夫|Julian Kostov}}、{{link-en|盧克·帕斯夸尼洛|Luke Pasqualino}}、{{link-en|潔絲敏·布萊克波羅|Jasmine Blackborow}}和{{link-en|加布里埃爾·布魯克斯|Gabrielle Brooks}}將出演常駐角色<ref>{{cite journal|url=https://deadline.com/2019/12/shadow-and-bone-netflix-series-cast-grishaverse-fantasy-novels-1202812257/|title='Shadow And Bone': Netflix Series Adds Seven To Cast|journal=Deadline|first=Denise|last=Petski|date=December 18, 2019|access-date=December 18, 2019|archive-date=2019-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191218184528/https://deadline.com/2019/12/shadow-and-bone-netflix-series-cast-grishaverse-fantasy-novels-1202812257/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 著名的書中人物尼古拉·蘭佐夫（Nikolai Lantsov）和維蘭·范·埃克（Wylan Van Eck）沒有出現在第一季<ref>{{cite web|url=https://bookstacked.com/book-to-film/shadow-and-bone-netflix-cast-nikolai-wylan/|title='Shadow and Bone' series reveals additional cast|website=BookStacked|first=Mary|last=Dempsey|date=December 23, 2019|access-date=February 19, 2020|archive-date=2020-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200219183525/https://bookstacked.com/book-to-film/shadow-and-bone-netflix-cast-nikolai-wylan/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。小說系列的作者李·芭度葛在第3集中飾演一名馬特拉凱造物法師<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/COLrhWslGRe/?hl=en|title=Cameo Day!|website=Instagram|date=April 27, 2021|access-date=June 11, 2021}}</ref>。

