=== 音樂 ===
{{link-en|喬瑟夫·特拉帕尼斯|Joseph Trapanese}}是本劇的作曲家<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://collider.com/shadow-and-bone-netflix-series-composer-joseph-trapanese/|title=Netflix’s ‘Shadow and Bone’ Series Lands Composer Joseph Trapanese|journal=Collider|first=Adam|last=Chitwood|date=2020-06-11|accessdate=2020-06-12|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227014426/https://collider.com/shadow-and-bone-netflix-series-composer-joseph-trapanese/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年10月，艾瑞克·赫瑟勒和李·芭度葛參加線上[[紐約動漫展|紐約動漫展]]的一個專家小組<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Polo|first=Susana|date=September 17, 2020|title=New York Comic Con 2020 unveils more panels from its all-digital con|url=https://www.polygon.com/entertainment/2020/9/9/21418267/new-york-comic-con-2020-schedule-panels-modok-animaniacs-walking-dead|access-date=September 18, 2020|journal=Polygon|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109052116/https://www.polygon.com/entertainment/2020/9/9/21418267/new-york-comic-con-2020-schedule-panels-modok-animaniacs-walking-dead|dead-url=no}}</ref>，釋出部分為本劇創作的音樂<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Templeton|first=Molly|date=October 10, 2020|title=Leigh Bardugo and Eric Heisserer Talk Shadow and Bone|url=https://www.tor.com/2020/10/10/leigh-bardugo-eric-heisserer-talk-shadow-and-bone/|access-date=October 11, 2020|journal=Tor|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204063946/https://www.tor.com/2020/10/10/leigh-bardugo-eric-heisserer-talk-shadow-and-bone/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。執行製作人喬許·貝瑞在2020年12月16日報導說，最終的混音已經完成<ref>{{cite tweet|number=1339226954134765573|title=Finished our last @shadowandbone_ sound mix!!! It’s coming....|first=Josh|last=Barry|user=JoshBarryLA|date=December 16, 2020|access-date=December 17, 2020|archive-date=December 17, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217161857/https://twitter.com/JoshBarryLA/status/1339226954134765573|url-status=live}}</ref>。

特拉帕尼斯用了11個月的時間完成了樂譜<ref>{{Cite journal|url=https://variety.com/2021/artisans/production/shadow-and-bone-music-netflix-1234957417/|title=How 'Shadow and Bone' Composer Joseph Trapanese Created Fantastical Music for Netflix's Take on the Grishaverse|journal=Variety|first=Jon|last=Burlingame|date=22 April 2021|access-date=22 April 2021|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506220149/https://variety.com/2021/artisans/production/shadow-and-bone-music-netflix-1234957417/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在接受《AwardsDaily》採訪時，他解釋了他是如何在封城期間做到這一點的，透過在[[Zoom|Zoom]]指揮管弦樂隊之間同時進行混合獨奏錄音<ref name="ad 1">{{Cite journal|url=https://www.awardsdaily.com/2021/04/22/composer-joseph-trapanese-draws-from-russian-slavic-influences-for-netflixs-shadow-and-bone/|title=Composer Joseph Trapanese Draws from Russian, Slavic Influences for Netflix's 'Shadow and Bone'|journal=AwardsDaily|first=Clarence|last=Moye|date=22 April 2021|access-date=22 April 2021|archive-date=2021-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428220001/https://www.awardsdaily.com/2021/04/22/composer-joseph-trapanese-draws-from-russian-slavic-influences-for-netflixs-shadow-and-bone/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。俄羅斯和斯拉夫音樂提供了樂譜靈感的基礎，芭度葛將[[谢尔盖·普罗科菲耶夫|謝爾蓋·普羅高菲夫]]和民間歌謠當作具體例子<ref>{{Cite journal|url=https://collider.com/shadow-and-bone-soundtrack-her-name-is-alina-starkov-joseph-trapanese/|title=Exclusive: Hear Alina's Theme From the 'Shadow and Bone' Soundtrack|journal=Collider|first=Carly|last=Lane|date=19 April 2021|access-date=22 April 2021|archive-date=2021-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210425200836/https://collider.com/shadow-and-bone-soundtrack-her-name-is-alina-starkov-joseph-trapanese/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。此外，還使用了其他音樂傳統的元素，例如[[甘美朗|甘美朗]]<ref name="ad 1"/>。

